name: Hemicyne portrait t shirt
description:
The Hemicyne are a  species that lives on the shores of the Black Sea. They're people that have the head of a dog and are incapable of speech.

White 100% cotton t shirt screen printed with a portrait of a hemicyne. A part man part dog native to the shores of the black sea.

name: Hoo: Dawn Of A New Era
description:
A Chinese Phoenix, the Hoo only appears at the beginning of a new era.

Limited edition of 20, signed and numbered, lino print of the mythical bird, the Hoo, with hand painted flame. Printed onto 160 GSM paper.

Please note that due to the nature of Lino printing each print is slightly different, and in ordering a print you except that the print displayed will differ to the one you receive.

Approx 27.5cm X 34cm.
